title: 863. Big Week 3 Games, 8 Trending Storylines, Standout Rookies & Favorite Performances
itunes:title: 863. Big Week 3 Games, 8 Trending Storylines, Standout Rookies & Favorite Performances
description:
Daniel Jeremiah, Bucky Brooks and Rhett Lewis look back at the weekend and all the action from Week 3 of the NFL season. The guys start by breaking down the big 3 games from Sunday. Next, the group hit on 8 trending storylines around the league. After that, the trio each give a standout rookie and also their favorite performance in Week 3. Then, the guys focus on the Eagles 9 sack game against the Commanders. To wrap up the show, the trio hit on a few takeaways from the college football weekend.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
